OL,3,CCumbria councils request delay to
OL,4,Cmayoral election
OL,6,FIf it can, both councils then still
OL,7,Fneed to make a formal decision to
OL,8,Fagree to a Mayoral Combined Authority,
OL,9,Fwhich would then require an election.
OL,11,FIn a letter requesting a deferral to
OL,12,FJim McMahon MP, Minister for English
OL,13,FDevolution and Local Governance, the
OL,14,Fcouncils state: "This request is made
OL,15,Fin the spirit of constructive
OL,16,Fpartnership and with a shared ambition
OL,17,Fto ensure the strongest possible
OL,18,Ffoundations for a successful new
OL,19,Fgovernance model that delivers for the
OL,20,Fpeople of Cumbria."
