OL,3,CCumbria councils request delay to
OL,4,Cmayoral election
OL,6,FLocal elections for Cumberland Council
OL,7,Fand Westmorland & Furness Council are
OL,8,Fboth scheduled for 2027.
OL,10,FThe two councils say holding a mayoral
OL,11,Felection on the same date would save
OL,12,Fsignificant resources - about #1
OL,13,Fmillion if held as a standalone
OL,14,Felection - and would result in a
OL,15,Fhigher voter turnout.
OL,17,FThey added that a deferral would also
OL,18,Fprovide more time to prepare for the
OL,19,Festablishment of a new combined
OL,20,Fauthority.
