OL,6,FIt was announced that Cumbria was
OL,7,Fincluded in the Government's
OL,8,FDevolution Priority Programme in
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FBoth councils were invited to join the
OL,12,FPriority Programme after earlier
OL,13,Fexpressing interest in exploring what
OL,14,Fgreater devolution of powers could
OL,15,Fmean in Cumbria.
