OL,3,CCumbria councils request delay to
OL,4,Cmayoral election
OL,6,FThe new Labour Government has set out
OL,7,Fits intention to widen devolution
OL,8,Facross England, giving regions more
OL,9,Fpowers and decision-making over
OL,10,Fmatters such as economic development,
OL,11,Ftransport, employment support,
OL,12,Fplanning, and housing.
OL,14,FThe Government has not yet reported
OL,15,Fback on the public consultation
OL,16,Fexercise it held earlier this year.
